profile: 'DNM Enterprises is a full service Construction Management & General Contracting company based out of Kamloops, BC. We strive to grow professionally & personally by connecting with the best Trades & Suppliers in the industry. We work closely with our Clients & our Teams, to ensure the best solutions, for every project, no matter the size or challenge. DNM is able to achieve consistent success with completion times & budgets by continuously updating our equipment, constantly improving the knowledge base of our teams & utilizing the newest construction technology, products & software. We take pride in our role as a “Builder of Communities.” If you are going to build, please build with us!'
